---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'June 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — NM Nonprofits"
  description="Privacy policy for NM Nonprofits — how we collect, use, and protect your information."
  noIndex={false}
>
  <div class="container-content py-16 max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-12">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <div class="space-y-10 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Overview</h2>
        <p>
          NM Nonprofits ("we," "us," or "our") operates nmnonprofits.com. This policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and the choices you have. We do not sell your personal information.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Information we collect</h2>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Information you provide</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 mb-4">
          <li>Organization details submitted through our listing form</li>
          <li>Email address if you contact us directly</li>
          <li>Account information if you claim or manage a listing</li>
        </ul>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Information collected automatically</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
          <li>Pages visited and search queries used on the site</li>
          <li>Browser type, device type, and general location (city/region level)</li>
          <li>Referral source (how you found the site)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4">
          We use Vercel Web Analytics for traffic measurement. This tool does not use cookies and does not track you across other websites.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">How we use your information</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
          <li>To display and maintain organization listings in the directory</li>
          <li>To respond to inquiries and support requests</li>
          <li>To improve the site based on usage patterns</li>
          <li>To send transactional emails (listing confirmations, update notifications) if you have submitted an organization</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4">We do not use your information for advertising or sell it to third parties.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Directory listings</h2>
        <p>
          Information about nonprofit organizations listed in our directory is sourced from public records (IRS filings, organization websites, press releases) and direct submissions. If your organization is listed and you need to update or remove information, contact us at <a href="mailto:corrections@nmnonprofits.com" class="text-turquoise-700 hover:underline">corrections@nmnonprofits.com</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          NM Nonprofits does not use tracking or advertising cookies. We may use a session cookie for login functionality if you manage a listing. Our analytics provider (Vercel) does not set cookies.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Third-party services</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Vercel</strong> — hosting and edge delivery</li>
          <li><strong>Neon</strong> — database infrastructure</li>
          <li><strong>Vercel Web Analytics</strong> — cookieless traffic analytics</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4">Each provider has its own privacy policy governing how they handle data.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Data retention</h2>
        <p>
          We retain listing information as long as it is accurate and the organization remains active. Contact us to request removal of your organization's data.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this policy periodically. The date at the top of this page reflects the most recent revision. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Privacy questions or data requests: <a href="mailto:hello@nmnonprofits.com" class="text-turquoise-700 hover:underline">hello@nmnonprofits.com</a>
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
